  • Fujitsu ScanSnap iX500 SuperSpeed USB 3.0/Wireless-N Desktop Scanner
  • General Features:
  • Color: Black
  • USB 3.0 or WiFi connectivity to a PC or Mac 
  • Scan wirelessly to iOS or Android mobile devices
  • ScanSnap Cloud
  • Fast Double-Sided scanning
  • One button searchable PDF creation
  • Advanced paper feeding system
  • Blazing 25ppm color scanning
  • 50-sheets Automatic Document Feeder (ADF)
  • Built-in GI microprocessor
  • Able to edit scanned images in various ways with Nuance Power PDF Standard for Windows / Nuance PDF Converter for Mac
  • Faster searchable PDF creation
  • More Quick Menu Productivity
  • Multi-feed Detection: Supported (Standard) ultrasonic multi-feed detection sensor
  • Paper Weight (thickness): 40 g/m2 to 209 g/m2 (11 lb. to 56 lb.)
  • Paper Chute Capacity: Maximum 50 sheets (A4, 80g/m2 or 21 lb.)
  • Specifications:
  • Scanner Type: Automatic Document Feeder (ADF), Duplex Scanning
  • Scanning Modes: Color, Grayscale, Monochrome, Automatic (color / grayscale / monochrome detection)
  • Image Sensor: Color CIS (Contact Image Sensor) x 2 (front / back)
  • Light Source: 3 Color LED (Red / Green / Blue)
  • Optical Resolution: 600 x 600 dots per inch (dpi)
  • Scanning Speed (A4 portrait):
  • Auto Mode: Simplex or Duplex, 25 pages per minute (ppm)
  • Normal Mode: Color & Grayscale 150 dpi, Monochrome 300 dpi, Simplex/Duplex, 25 ppm
  • Better Mode: Color & Grayscale 200 dpi, Monochrome 400 dpi, Simplex/Duplex, 25 ppm
  • Best Mode: Color & Grayscale 300 dpi, Monochrome 600 dpi, Simplex/Duplex, 25 ppm
  • Excellent Mode: Color & Grayscale 600 dpi, Monochrome 1200 dpi, Simplex/Duplex, 7 ppm
  • Document Size:
  • Normal Mode without Carrier Sheet: A4, A5, A6, B5, B6, Business Card, Post Card, Letter, Legal and Custom Size.
  • Max: 216 mm X 360 mm (8.5 in. X 14.17 in.), Min: 50.8 mm X 50.8 mm (2 in. X 2 n.). Automatically recognizes document size.
  • Normal Mode with Carrier Sheet: Use of a Carrier Sheet permits the scanning of A3, B4, 279.4 mm X 431.8 mm (11 in. x 17 in.) and photographs as well as the document sizes listed above. Long Paper Scanning: 863mm (34 in.)
  • Interface:
  • SuperSpeed USB 3.0 (USB 2.0/1.1 compatible)
  • Wi-Fi Interface: Standards: IEEE802.11b / IEEE802.11g / IEEE802.11n
    • Communication Mode: Infrastructure Mode
    • Frequency: 2.412 GHz to 2.462 GHz / 2.412 GHz to 2.472 GHz
    • Communication Distance: Indoors, 50 m (Recommended: indoors, within 25 m)
    • Security: WPA-PSK (TKIP / AES), WPA2-PSK (TKIP / AES),  WEP (64-bit / 128-bit)
  • Power Adapter Specifications:
  • Input: 100-240V, 50/60Hz
  • Output: 16V, 2.5A
  • Dimensions:
  • 6.6 x 11.5 x 6.2-inches (H x W x D, approximate)
  • Weight: 6.62 lbs. / 3.0kg
  • Fujitsu ScanSnap iX500 Wireless Desktop Scanner
  • Nunance PDF Standard/Converter Software for PC & Mac
  • Setup DVD-ROM
  • Carrier Sheet
  • USB 3.0 cable
  • Power adapter
  • Power cord

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
